        "hizbQuarter": 15,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 246,
        "text": "If you fear (war or danger), pray while standing or on horseback; but when you have safety again remember God, for He taught you what you did not know.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 2,
          "name": "سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Baqara",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Cow",
          "revelationType": "Medinan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 286
        },
        "numberInSurah": 239,
        "juz": 2,
        "manzil": 1,
        "page": 39,
        "ruku": 32,
        "hizbQuarter": 15,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 247,
        "text": "Those among you about to die leaving wives behind, should bequeath a year's maintenance and lodging for them, without expelling them from home. But if they leave (of their own accord), you will not be blamed for what they do with themselves in their own rights. God is all-mighty and all-wise.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 2,
          "name": "سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Baqara",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Cow",
          "revelationType": "Medinan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 286
        },
        "numberInSurah": 240,
        "juz": 2,
        "manzil": 1,
        "page": 39,
        "ruku": 32,
        "hizbQuarter": 15,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 248,
        "text": "Making a fair provision for women who are divorced is the duty of those who are God-fearing and pious.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 2,
          "name": "سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Baqara",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Cow",
          "revelationType": "Medinan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 286
        },
        "numberInSurah": 241,
        "juz": 2,
        "manzil": 1,
        "page": 39,
        "ruku": 32,
        "hizbQuarter": 15,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 249,
        "text": "So does God pronounce His decrees that you may understand.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 2,
          "name": "سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Baqara",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Cow",
          "revelationType": "Medinan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 286
        },
        "numberInSurah": 242,
        "juz": 2,
        "manzil": 1,
        "page": 39,
        "ruku": 32,
        "hizbQuarter": 15,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 250,
        "text": "Have you never thought of men who went out of their homes as a measure of safety against death, and they were thousands, to whom God said: \"Die,\" then restored them to life? Indeed God bestows His blessings on men; only most men are not grateful.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 2,
          "name": "سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Baqara",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Cow",
          "revelationType": "Medinan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 286
        },
        "numberInSurah": 243,
        "juz": 2,
        "manzil": 1,
        "page": 39,
        "ruku": 33,
        "hizbQuarter": 16,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 251,
        "text": "Fight in the way of God, and remember that God hears all and knows everything.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 2,
          "name": "سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ",
          "englishName": "Al-Baqara",
          "englishNameTranslation": "The Cow",
          "revelationType": "Medinan",
          "numberOfAyahs": 286
        },
        "numberInSurah": 244,
        "juz": 2,
        "manzil": 1,
        "page": 39,
        "ruku": 33,
        "hizbQuarter": 16,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 252,
        "text": "Who will give a goodly loan to God which He might double many times? For God withholds and enlarges, and to Him you will return.",
        "surah": {
          "number": 2,
          "name": "سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ",
